  m_TableData:
  - m_Id: 1
    m_Localized: 'Why do the most beautiful fish always go for the biggest sharks?
      it is literally biology

'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2
    m_Localized: No one cares about the pain of young male sharks anymore
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 3
    m_Localized: 'Because I tell young sharks to question everything, work hard and
      get as rich as possible I get banned '
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 4
    m_Localized: Gentleshark, understand this. You are not hardwired in your egg
      to be certain type. Just make the right choices
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 5
    m_Localized: RedShark Redemption 2 is a bit woke, innit?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 6
    m_Localized: 'No shark is perfect, we all fall short ... (Finicus 3:23) but its
      important to know & see your bad habits. '
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 7
    m_Localized: If it wasnt for males, Taylor Swims had nothing to sing about
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 8
    m_Localized: Overswim should do something about those e-daters, its disgusting,
      keep the females of our game
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 9
    m_Localized: Meryl Reef kinda let herself go in Bitcraft movie trailer, huh?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 10
    m_Localized: Its so hard being a shark nowadays when all these females keep attacking
      you for no reason
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 11
    m_Localized: Females that are into Straypups are such a red flag
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 12
    m_Localized: 'Lil Nas Shark really calls himself a rapper and then kisses other
      males '
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 13
    m_Localized: Why do smaller fish and female sharks always swim in groups when
      I show up???
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 14
    m_Localized: Gentlesharks, always remember that if you can smell blood in the
      water to go for the kill
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 15
    m_Localized: A true gentleshark never gives up! #truealpha #gentleshark
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 16
    m_Localized: Sharkbowl truly is the only event where there are still real sharks
      playing
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 17
    m_Localized: Sabrina Sharkenter is really out there telling all male sharks they
      are useless, huh?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 18
    m_Localized: Female sharks really expect a great white but bring nothing to the
      ocean themselves
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 19
    m_Localized: The ocean does not reward kindness it rewards strength #AlwaysHas
      #AlwaysWill
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
